  "analyst_note": "CVE-2023-46805 + CVE-2024-21887: Chained authentication bypass + command injection in Ivanti Connect Secure and Policy Secure. Exploited by UNC5221 (Chinese nexus) since Dec 2023. The /dana-na/ path and DSID= cookies are characteristic of Ivanti Connect Secure (formerly Pulse Connect Secure). If Ivanti is confirmed, check CISA emergency directive ED 24-01 mitigations. Apply Ivanti's integrity checker tool (ICT) to detect compromise. Fixed: varies by version track. Note: Ivanti released delayed patches; apply immediately upon availability.",
